{"word":"G581 - ἀπογενόμενος - apogenómenos - ap-og-en-om'-en-os - Being dead","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπογενόμενος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apogenómenos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-og-en-om'-en-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Being dead</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செத்துப்போ"},{"paragraph":"1. to be removed from, depart"},{"paragraph":"2. to die"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Past participle of a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1096 - γίνομαι - gínomai - ghin'-om-ahee/1096\">G1096</a>; <i>absent</i>, that is, <i>deceased</i> (figuratively <i>renounced</i>): - being dead.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1078/1078\">G1078</a>, <a href=\"#/G1081/1081\">G1081</a>, <a href=\"#/G1085/1085\">G1085</a>, <a href=\"#/G1096/1096\">G1096</a>, <a href=\"#/G3824/3824\">G3824</a>, <a href=\"#/G581/581\">G581</a>"}]}